<article>
    <h4>Points</h4>
    <p>
        <b>Segment Completion:</b> Each ride earns a total point value based on mileage and elevation. Segment details
        can be found on the <a href="/bikeroutes">Bike Routes</a> page. Remember, only one segment per ride.
    </p>
    <p>
        <b>Attackers:</b> The first three finishers of each segment receive bonus points:
    <ul>
        <li>🥇 1st place: +5 points</li>
        <li>🥈 2nd place: +3 points</li>
        <li>🥉 3rd place: +1 point</li>
    </ul>
    Bonus points are awarded separately for W/T/F and Male categories. Note: Rankings are based on submission date, not
    ride date—so submit your rides promptly to maximize points!
    </p>
    <p>
        <b>Time Bonus:</b> The main Adventure Series does not include time-based bonuses. However, we occasionally host
        Strava Segment Challenges with prizes. Join our <a href="https://www.strava.com/clubs/redwoodadventurecycling"
            target="_blank">Strava Club</a> to stay updated.
    </p>
</article>

